{"tid":1474443,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【手足必修課】Winter On Fire 烏克蘭革命 - 武力升級過程同香港幾乎一樣","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:47:23.000Z","uid":27718,"like":123,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c874aebe2aa2c1ccae6d1488c99fdfe37688ae","tid":1474443,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:30:48.000Z","msg":"凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰- Netflix<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTY4MDgwOTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMjU3NjE@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BNTY4MDgwOTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMjU3NjE%40._V1_.jpg&h=3cd7b9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Fhk%2Ftitle%2F80031666&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=eb737781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666</a></blockquote><br />\n紀錄片 - 2014年的烏克蘭EuroMaidan革命<br />\n片中有大量記者和烏克蘭人拍攝的片段，<br />\n有示威者現場被實彈擊中的片段，<br />\n亦有在戰場上生還的烏克蘭人接受採訪。<br />\n<br />\n黑警既情況 簡直有啲似香港既預言書<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">下載連結喺最底</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭：<br />\n1.和平集會抗議被黑警暴力驅散<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drLhxag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrLhxag.jpg&h=b1b10900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vamkuWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvamkuWX.jpg&h=d1eeb97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTYV3g3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTYV3g3.jpg&h=16d168e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.搵黑社會扮示威者作<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暴力挑釁+安插內鬼+警黑合作</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEBAiQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEBAiQp.jpg&h=9d4f4896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.警棍放題，跌低繼續打，每個黑警經過都補幾棍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3cjLvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3cjLvx.jpg&h=bf2a0bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnSzzoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnSzzoT.jpg&h=62158d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-人民開始戴頭盔返工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkdCxaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkdCxaZ.jpg&h=8a422fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.有示威者被橡膠子彈射爆眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cf1sUpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCf1sUpu.jpg&h=65123cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.急救員、現場醫生超近距離被惡意槍擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5E97N7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5E97N7.jpg&h=99df00ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4QtDRg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4QtDRg.jpg&h=fc8ef565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.加料 - 黑警在震撼彈中加入螺絲、金屬，增加殺傷力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hd7f3h0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhd7f3h0.jpg&h=1d125f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\nN.第一個中槍的死士出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngsGYRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngsGYRr.jpg&h=3a0fbf80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nN+1.手持鐵盾的示威者開始被實彈射殺，數天內被黑警射殺超過一百人，革命中有大量人士被失縱<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzYODRw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzYODRw.jpg&h=d635d71c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owySk4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowySk4S.jpg&h=91bc6fe7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnh0uYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxnh0uYg.jpg&h=6a168efc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n...<br />\n2015年，烏克蘭東部與俄羅斯戰爭，至今仍未結束<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOeaSbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOeaSbK.jpg&h=19014d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgRMqwL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgRMqwL.jpg&h=db3cdb79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n每個打壓既階段，都同我地現況好相似<br />\n想知烏克蘭人係點樣革命？<br />\n睇全片啦<br />\n<br />\n片長：約90分鐘，絕無冷場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">-本文重點-</span></strong></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">全片---(內掛中文字幕 - 720p.mkv)[推薦，必需下載]：\nhttps://drive.google.com/open?id=1NtJhOrTMt7PmmRNXFOLXkyK11q49yXDT\n\n全片---(刻印中文字幕 - 720p.mp4)[重複壓制較低清，可線上看]：\nhttps://drive.google.com/open?id=1Zxf89PKjFUoFL-27HLfe7e0QrNAIFClI\n\n如果流量超出限制，請製作副本到自己的Google Drive再下載。</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">無字幕原片720p.mp4+高登中文外掛字幕srt (HKG財經台Gdrive):\nhttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0Bwb5J1CwZ5KVZ1p1RkFUZVZEdEU\n更新中文字幕srt:\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/0B5cYR0h_uLP7b2pieWJybUtyc3M/view\n高登字幕巴打原文：\nhttps://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/6248238/page/1\nHKG財經台轉自原文：\nhttps://lihkg.com/thread/1201430/page/1</code></pre><br />\n感謝所有為本片字幕付出時間既巴打絲打手足。"},{"pid":"1344b1b1d2e8e4d4ec90762f3d0c179c62cffbfd","tid":1474443,"uid":78957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"大家準備好未？"},{"pid":"de2188760e2c67c51dac61632c24f359278b0bd3","tid":1474443,"uid":27718,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1344b1b1d2e8e4d4ec90762f3d0c179c62cffbfd","tid":1474443,"uid":78957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"大家準備好未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"革命既代價"},{"pid":"5856ef762142339f3216eb54fd70e7e61393a9eb","tid":14744