"uid":171450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:46:48.000Z","msg":"要死人"},{"pid":"b16077b987eec1a1a6b354d8c92de2f418ee5ccf","tid":1474443,"uid":221627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"睇完真係覺得個劇本係一樣"},{"pid":"8ba2a0d6bbefe0dfe423a7209eb4a8dfc7e5f899","tid":1474443,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"嗰時都有好多人親俄，但親俄嗰啲人淨係識網上面鬧"},{"pid":"2925245ee95ab7cc3a2d83289479cd4fdb45fdd4","tid":1474443,"uid":27718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"民意？企得出黎嗰啲先叫民意<br />\n喱喺屋企係無人會理"},{"pid":"71f493b8e796cfd64890b019f1a0c84bd0634906","tid":1474443,"uid":111576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"根本係一樣，極權嘅適用性係全世界，大家做好準備未？winter on fire 我睇左兩次，都係喊到仆街，好似睇到香港嘅未來。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油！香港人！</span>"},{"pid":"11471ff7f60cb0e52856fd424b122467f3af36c3","tid":1474443,"uid":27718,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWyySWN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWyySWN.gif&h=b39a839e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪似曾相識"},{"pid":"8e89764ab839c46d0d9ea7b0ed76c71b2346793f","tid":1474443,"uid":100714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"佢哋犧牲咗好多人命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639b32527e32efbab8451759ac1fdc5978cd580d","tid":1474443,"uid":271857,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭不是國際金融中心。<br />\n香港金融大佬要傾惦數先得，<br />\n不過相信啲大佬都唔鍾意老共，<br />\n成日收巿點數都係故意串爆大陸。<br />\n解放軍只係識打人民，<br />\n剩係用權威來壓人民邊會有人服<br />\n正宗華人教仔方式<br />\n唔講道理，所以華人成長中都有點心理不平衡。<br />\n長大咗又用返同一手法來宣洩俾仔女<br />\n一代傳一代。<br />\n華人失敗就係封閉式思維，<br />\n無創意